{"ja513:0.1":"Jataka ","ja513:0.2":"Timsanipata ","ja513:0.3":"Kimchandavagga ","ja513:0.4":"3. Jayaddisajataka ","ja513:1.1":"“Cirassam vata me udapadi ajja, ","ja513:1.2":"Bhakkho maha sattamibhattakale; ","ja513:1.3":"Kutosi ko vasi tadingha bruhi, ","ja513:1.4":"Acikkha jatim vidito yathasi”. ","ja513:2.1":"“Pancalaraja migavam pavittho, ","ja513:2.2":"Jayaddiso nama yadissuto te; ","ja513:2.3":"Carami kacchani vanani caham, ","ja513:2.4":"Pasadam imam khada mamajja munca”. ","ja513:3.1":"“Seneva tvam panasi sassamano, ","ja513:3.2":"Mamesa bhakkho pasado yam vadesi; ","ja513:3.3":"Tam khadiyana pasadam jighannam, ","ja513:3.4":"Khadissam paccha na vilapakalo”. ","ja513:4.1":"“Na catthi mokkho mama nikkayena, ","ja513:4.2":"Gantvana paccagamanaya panhe; ","ja513:4.3":"Tam sangaram brahmanassappadaya, ","ja513:4.4":"Saccanurakkhi punaravajissam”. ","ja513:5.1":"“Kim kammajatam anutappate tvam, ","ja513:5.2":"Pattam samipam maranassa raja; ","ja513:5.3":"Acikkha me tam api sakkunemu, ","ja513:5.4":"Anujanitum agamanaya panhe”. ","ja513:6.1":"“Kata maya brahmanassa dhanasa, ","ja513:6.2":"Tam sangaram patimukkam na muttam; ","ja513:6.3":"Tam sangaram brahmanassappadaya, ","ja513:6.4":"Saccanurakkhi punaravajissam”. ","ja513:7.1":"“Ya te kata brahmanassa dhanasa, ","ja513:7.2":"Tam sangaram patimukkam na muttam; ","ja513:7.3":"Tam sangaram brahmanassappadaya, ","ja513:7.4":"Saccanurakkhi punaravajassu”. ","ja513:8.1":"Mutto ca so porisadassa hattha, ","ja513:8.2":"Gantva sakam mandiram kamakami; ","ja513:8.3":"Tam sangaram brahmanassappadaya, ","ja513:8.4":"Amantayi puttamalinasattam. ","ja513:9.1":"“Ajjeva rajjam abhisincayassu, ","ja513:9.2":"Dhammam cara sesu paresu capi; ","ja513:9.3":"Adhammakaro ca te mahu ratthe, ","ja513:9.4":"Gacchamaham porisadassa natte”. ","ja513:10.1":"“Kim kamma kubbam tava deva pava, ","ja513:10.2":"Naradhayi tam tadicchami sotum; ","ja513:10.3":"Yamajja rajjamhi udassaye tuvam, ","ja513:10.4":"Rajjampi niccheyyam taya vinaham”. ","ja513:11.1":"“Na kammuna va vacasa va tata, ","ja513:11.2":"Aparadhitoham tuviyam sarami; ","ja513:11.3":"Sandhinca katva purisadakena, ","ja513:11.4":"Saccanurakkhi punaham gamissam”. ","ja513:12.1":"“Aham gamissami idheva hohi, ","ja513:12.2":"Natthi tato jivato vippamokkho; ","ja513:12.3":"Sace tuvam gacchasiyeva raja, ","ja513:12.4":"Ahampi gacchami ubho na homa”. ","ja513:13.1":"“Addha hi tata satanesa dhammo, ","ja513:13.2":"Marana ca me dukkhataram tadassa; ","ja513:13.3":"Kammasapado tam yada pacitva, ","ja513:13.4":"Pasayha khade bhida rukkhasule”. ","ja513:14.1":"“Panena te panamaham nimissam, ","ja513:14.2":"Ma tvam aga porisadassa natte; ","ja513:14.3":"Etanca te panamaham nimissam, ","ja513:14.4":"Tasma matam jivitassa vannemi”. ","ja513:15.1":"Tato have dhitima rajaputto, ","ja513:15.2":"Vanditva matu ca pitu ca pade; ","ja513:15.3":"Dukhinissa mata nipata pathabya, ","ja513:15.4":"Pitassa paggayha bhujani kandati. ","ja513:16.1":"Tam gacchantam tava pita viditva, ","ja513:16.2":"Parammukho vandati panjaliko; ","ja513:16.3":"“Somo ca raja varuno ca raja, ","ja513:16.4":"Pajapati candima suriyo ca; ","ja513:16.5":"Etehi gutto purisadakamha, ","ja513:16.6":"Anunnato sotthi paccehi tata”. ","ja513:17.1":"“Yam dandakiranno gatassa mata, ","ja513:17.2":"Ramassakasi sotthanam sugutta; ","ja513:17.3":"Tam te aham sotthanam karomi, ","ja513:17.4":"Etena saccena sarantu deva; ","ja513:17.5":"Anunnato sotthi paccehi putta”. ","ja513:18.1":"“Avi raho vapi manopadosam, ","ja513:18.2":"Naham sare jatu malinasatte; ","ja513:18.3":"Etena saccena sarantu deva, ","ja513:18.4":"Anunnato sotthi paccehi bhatika”. ","ja513:19.1":"“Yasma ca me anadhimanosi sami, ","ja513:19.2":"Na capi me manasa appiyosi; ","ja513:19.3":"Etena saccena sarantu deva, ","ja513:19.4":"Anunnato sotthi paccehi sami”. ","ja513:20.1":"“Braha uju carumukho kutosi, ","ja513:20.2":"Na mam pajanasi vane vasantam; ","ja513:20.3":"Luddam mam natva ‘purisadako’ti, ","ja513:20.4":"Ko sotthimajanamidhavajeyya”. ","ja513:21.1":"“Janami ludda purisadako tvam, ","ja513:21.2":"Na tam na janami vane vasantam; ","ja513:21.3":"Ahanca puttosmi jayaddisassa, ","ja513:21.4":"Mamajja khada pituno pamokkha”. ","ja513:22.1":"“Janami puttoti jayaddisassa, ","ja513:22.2":"Tatha hi vo mukhavanno ubhinnam; ","ja513:22.3":"Sudukkaranneva katam tavedam, ","ja513:22.4":"Yo mattumicche pituno pamokkha”. ","ja513:23.1":"“Na dukkaram kinci mahettha manne, ","ja513:23.2":"Yo mattumicche pituno pamokkha; ","ja513:23.3":"Matu ca hetu paraloka gantva, ","ja513:23.4":"Sukhena saggena ca sampayutto”. ","ja513:24.1":"“Ahanca kho attano papakiriyam, ","ja513:24.2":"Avi raho vapi sare na jatu; ","ja513:24.3":"Sankhatajatimaranohamasmi, ","ja513:24.4":"Yatheva me idha tatha parattha. ","ja513:25.1":"Khadajja mam dani mahanubhava, ","ja513:25.2":"Karassu kiccani imam sariram; ","ja513:25.3":"Rukkhassa va te papatami agga, ","ja513:25.4":"Chadayamano mayham tvamadesi mamsam”. ","ja513:26.1":"“Idanca te ruccati rajaputta, ","ja513:26.2":"Cajesi panam pituno pamokkha; ","ja513:26.3":"Tasma hi so tvam taramanarupo, ","ja513:26.4":"Sambhanja katthani jalehi aggim”. ","ja513:27.1":"Tato have dhitima rajaputto, ","ja513:27.2":"Darum samahatva mahantamaggim; ","ja513:27.3":"Sandipayitva pativedayittha, ","ja513:27.4":"“Adipito dani mahayamaggi”. ","ja513:28.1":"“Khadajja mam dani pasayhakari, ","ja513:28.2":"Kim mam muhum pekkhasi hatthalomo; ","ja513:28.3":"Tatha tatha tuyhamaham karomi, ","ja513:28.4":"Yatha yatha mam chadayamano adesi”. ","ja513:29.1":"“Ko tadisam arahati khaditaye, ","ja513:29.2":"Dhamme thitam saccavadim vadannum; ","ja513:29.3":"Muddhapi tassa viphaleyya sattadha, ","ja513:29.4":"Yo tadisam saccavadim adeyya”. ","ja513:30.1":"“Idanhi so brahmanam mannamano, ","ja513:30.2":"Saso avasesi sake sarire; ","ja513:30.3":"Teneva so candima devaputto, ","ja513:30.4":"Sasatthuto kamaduhajja yakkha”. ","ja513:31.1":"“Cando yatha rahumukha pamutto, ","ja513:31.2":"Virocate pannaraseva bhanuma; ","ja513:31.3":"Evam tuvam porisada pamutto, ","ja513:31.4":"Viroca kapile mahanubhava; ","ja513:31.5":"Amodayam pitaram mataranca, ","ja513:31.6":"Sabbo ca te nandatu natipakkho”. ","ja513:32.1":"Tato have dhitima rajaputto, ","ja513:32.2":"Katanjali pariyaya porisadam; ","ja513:32.3":"Anunnato sotthi sukhi arogo, ","ja513:32.4":"Paccagama kapilamalinasatto. ","ja513:33.1":"Tam negama janapada ca sabbe, ","ja513:33.2":"Hattharoha rathika pattika ca; ","ja513:33.3":"Namassamana panjalika upagamum, ","ja513:33.4":"“Namatthu te dukkarakarakosi”ti. ","ja513:34.1":"Jayaddisajatakam tatiyam. "}